Api Documentation

General Information

Base URL = https://cryptofertas.tk/backend/api.php
method = GET
Functions= readOwner, readProvider, writeDirty.


Function Information




Function ReadOwner

Params send:
	function= readOwner
	param= wallet of the owner you want to fetch the NFT from

Calling example:
	https://cryptofertas.tk/backend/api.php?function=readOwner&param=0xe0eb47219eebfd3aa646bfa6b1cff194ab0397da

Result example:

