Function ReadProvider

Params send:
	function= readProvider
	param= wallet of the provider you want to fetch the NFT from

Calling example:
	https://cryptofertas.tk/backend/api.php?function=readProvider&param=0x06eb67071a06e676b678f5dd3614d852c129d460

